44
00:06:59,132 --> 00:07:00,804
This is an express elevator.

45
00:07:00,892 --> 00:07:02,564
The only way in or out
is through access panels.

46
00:07:02,652 --> 00:07:04,768
The bomber's also wired
the hatch to trigger the bomb,...

47
00:07:04,852 --> 00:07:07,889
...which seats him
in the 'crazy but not stupid' section.

48
00:07:07,972 --> 00:07:10,964
Sir, Harry volunteers to examine the device.

49
00:07:11,052 --> 00:07:12,201
Yeah, right.

50
00:07:12,292 --> 00:07:13,486
Fine.

51
00:07:13,572 --> 00:07:15,210
The two of you check it out.

52
00:07:15,292 --> 00:07:17,965
The nearest access panel's
on the 32nd floor in the lobby.

53
00:07:18,052 --> 00:07:20,168
I want reports only.
We're in a holding pattern.

54
00:07:20,252 --> 00:07:22,083
Worthy, Briggs,
I want you to secure the base area.

55
00:07:22,172 --> 00:07:22,843
No-one in or out.

56
00:07:22,932 --> 00:07:25,685
Everyone else,
I want you to affirm building evac. Move!

57
00:07:26,772 --> 00:07:27,648
Looks like we're walking.

58
00:07:28,612 --> 00:07:30,523
Hurry, folks, but watch your step!

59
00:07:30,612 --> 00:07:31,647
29.

60
00:07:31,732 --> 00:07:34,804
All the way down to the lobby!
Let's go, folks!

61
00:07:34,892 --> 00:07:36,769
30.

62
00:07:38,252 --> 00:07:39,924
31.

63
00:07:42,292 --> 00:07:43,407
32.

